749
00:56:17,139 --> 00:56:18,610
How are you so sure?

750
00:56:26,880 --> 00:56:27,949
Because if you saw his face,

751
00:56:30,219 --> 00:56:31,790
there's no way you wouldn't know.

752
00:56:35,730 --> 00:56:36,790
There's no way...

753
00:56:39,060 --> 00:56:41,469
