760
00:57:22,569 --> 00:57:24,710
I wanted him to stay warm.

761
00:57:28,009 --> 00:57:29,650
I made it myself.

762
00:57:33,650 --> 00:57:34,650
Do you think...

763
00:57:37,589 --> 00:57:39,259
